cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SE

The paper focuses on security monitoring and intrusion detection in distributed high throughput computing systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The use of deep learning methods for real-time data analysis suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The implementation of a prototype system also suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE).
